These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
House: craftsman, cottage, townhouse, victorian
There 4 different types of food: garlic, cranberry, lime, tomato
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, cycling, cricket, climbing
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, video-games, fishing
1. the person who's sport is cycling is the person eating tomato##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is between the townhouse house and the victorian house##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the townhouse house##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the victorian house##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
9. the cottage house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House   | cottage | victorian   | craftsman  | townhouse  |
| Food   | cranberry    | tomato    | garlic      | lime    |
| Sport   | climbing | cycling | cricket | soccer |
| Hobby     | fishing  | card-games       | photography    | video-games     |

