.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, white, amber, aquamarine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, montecristo, baccarat, aristoff
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, electrician, firefighter, security-guard
City: marseilles, hannover, prague, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
3. the security-guard is the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is between the firefighter and the person traveling to marseilles##2
6. the person traveling to colone is between the aristoff-smoker and the security-guard##2
7. the nurse is on the far right##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | aquamarine | white    | amber  | apricot    |
| Cigar   | old-henry      | montecristo  | aristoff  | baccarat |
| Job           | security-guard      | firefighter       | electrician      | nurse       |
| City         | hannover    | colone | prague | marseilles |

