.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, thriller, satire
4 different pets are kept: snake, horse, bird, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, electronic, disco, gospel
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, purple, apricot, emerald
1. the fan disco is the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the fan gospel##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the fan electronic is the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the hedgehog##2
9. the owner of the bird is between the person watching thriller movies and the fan electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre        | western | thriller     | time-travel   | satire     |
| Pet       | horse   | snake   | bird | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre         | techno   | disco | gospel       | electronic    |
| Color   | apricot    | purple | red  | emerald    |

