 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who likes mauve##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
10. the person who likes lilac is between the person playing go and the person who likes apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Color           | turquise  | apricot | lilac     | mauve |
| Hobby   | cooking | writing  | hiking | reading       |
| Game           | bridge       | chess    | whist      | go           |
