 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the fan metal is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan metal##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the fan classical##1
 9. the person who growspoppy is between the person traveling to rome and the fan pop##2
10. the fan house is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
