.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, old-henry, cain, prince
City: paris, marseilles, london, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, 7up, mirinda
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, bird, rat
1. the person traveling to paris is between the owner of the rat and the person traveling to london##2
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person traveling to paris and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person drinking 7up is between the owner of the ferret and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | cain | old-henry | fonseca  | prince |
| City   | marseilles      | new-york       | paris     | london      |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | almond-milk      | 7up   | soy-milk   |
| Pet         | bird   | rat    | mouse | ferret   |

