4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, aristoff, bluemaster
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the aristoff-smoker##2
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Transport      | train      | snowmobile     | bus    | subway |
| Sport   | tennis | lacrosse | cricket      | golf     |
| Hobby   | singing    | fishing       | woodworking    | chess         |
